  <name>Hyphanet</name>
  <summary>Anonymizing peer-to-peer network</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Hyphanet (formerly Freenet) is a peer-to-peer platform for censorship-resistant communication.
      It uses a decentralized distributed data store to keep and deliver information, and has a suite of free software for publishing and communicating on the Web without fear of censorship.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse websites anonymously</li>
      <li>Publish your own websites (Freesites)</li>
      <li>Chat on forums and message boards</li>
      <li>Share files securely</li>
      <li>Decentralized and censorship-resistant</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
